text.header1: Fungura amahuza Yizewe kandi atazwi ukoresheje Kasm Gufungura-muri-Kwigunga.
text.header2: Kasm Gufungura muri Kwagura Mucukumbuzi ya Isolation itanga iburyo-ukanda menu kugirango ufungure imiyoboro y'urubuga muri Workspace yihariye ya mushakisha. Ibi bituma byoroha kandi bidafite aho bihuriye no gufungura URL ziteye inkeke / umutekano muke cyangwa kubungabunga ubuzima bwawe bwite. Kubera ko urubuga rutangwa imbere ya mushakisha ya kure yumwanya wakazi, aho gukorerwa kuri mudasobwa yawe, urashobora gukora neza kandi utazwi gukorana nurubuga.
text.header3: Reba inyandiko ya Kasm kubindi bisobanuro.

title.tooltip1: Genda uzafungura URL mumwanya mushya wakazi, uburyo bwa Cast Key nuburyo bukoreshwa
title.tooltip2: Iyo ufunguye inyandiko mumasomo ya Kasm keretse niba umurongo ari URL yemewe bizanyuzwa kuri moteri ishakisha
title.tooltip3: Niba gufungura inyandiko mumwanya wakazi urashobora gushaka gusimbuza imirongo yanyuze kumurimo (Shakisha ishyigikira RegExp isanzwe hamwe na delimiters / regexp / g)
